data.description:
55? You're Lucky!
You qualify to live in Conquistador, a fun place with all the amenities and a short distance to area beaches, dining, shopping and downtown Stuart.  This second-floor condo with elevator access features 2 bedrooms, 2 full baths and washer/dryer and the building just finished the new roof replacement. Kitchen upgraded, laminate wood floors in main areas.  Community amenities are covered under the HOA fee.  An active community with a community pool overlooking the waterway, an active clubhouse, tennis, etc.  Fishing and seating area right on the waterway.  Gated community offers privacy and security.
